{"tid":2216000,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO5+1 擴大至1BNO持有人97年後出生成年人子女，其配偶及未滿18歲子女","createTime":"2020-09-24T10:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T04:55:00.000Z","uid":140538,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cc40a5d2f5459906f6890d9e02a1c9292b4725d6","tid":2216000,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:58:38.000Z","msg":"英國內政部就BNO持有人申請在英國逗留的指引，在星期二9月22日作出了更新，主要涉及兩點：<br />\n一、可透過「5+1」最終申請居英權的合資格人士，由BNO持有人、其配偶及未滿18歲子女，進一步擴大至BNO持有人的1997年7月1日或以後出生的成年人子女，以及那些成人子女的配偶及未成年子女。至此，只餘下英治時期已出生、儘管合資格但因當時父母未有替他申領BNO的香港人，未能受惠這計劃。<br />\n二、如何在有關BNO簽證計劃明年元旦正式實施前，現時透過酌情留英（LOTR）來暫時獲准逗留英國，指引提供更清晰的解釋，包括需要提供什麼文件。"},{"pid":"5e3f7c924291a2b830865f8d2c565e88c0b99e91","tid":2216000,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fbritish-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=52856d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"bf8869c243a59825961365b1ce3bfb12042b658a","tid":2216000,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890149bafeb50f25c05da0b244d56b6ab38517c9","tid":2216000,"uid":19012,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n<br />\n有幾多個97年後出世既咁快結婚生仔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（比盡得23歲）<br />\n<br />\n唔計腥港人 以生蟲既速度有下一代"},{"pid":"7a2d933e66741558e93a13a4e3d5313608d60ba8","tid":2216000,"uid":198856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"97後出世應該冇bno嫁<br />\n係咪講緊BNO持有人嘅97後出生子女？"},{"pid":"5e2d2f468ae8c5423c650660ab8f8